<activity xml:id="act-situacionesEcuacionesYDiagramas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>A and F B, D, and L C, H, and J E and G I and K</p>
<p>Sample response: I know that B, D, and L match because the bar of 225 represents the box of 225 paper clips and the 7 boxes of 10 represent the paper clips in the notebooks. To know how many paper clips Elena has, we would have to add all of this up, which is shown in the equation and in the diagram.</p>
  </solution>


